to tell you

43:32.023 --> 43:33.438
that even though
you thought

43:33.472 --> 43:35.785
your dad was away
on a long business trip,

43:35.820 --> 43:38.788
the truth is that he's actually
moved out of the house.

43:38.823 --> 43:39.824
