43:42.758 --> 43:43.759
Kenny!

43:45.484 --> 43:47.590
-It's gonna be fine, Nate.
-[NATE SOBBING QUIETLY]

43:47.625 --> 43:48.798
Stop crying.

43:48.833 --> 43:50.731
Tell him
it's gonna be fine, Dad.

43:50.766 --> 43:52.422
Tell him
you're coming back home.

43:52.457 --> 43:54.701
Your father can't
tell you that, Joshua,

43:54.735 --> 43:56.875
because your father
has found a new woman.

43:56.910 --> 43:58.670
