44:22.349 --> 44:24.454
We don't go
to an actually school, Dad.

44:24.489 --> 44:27.423
But-but you have--
You have friends, right?

44:27.457 --> 44:28.700
You mean
realm buddies?

44:28.735 --> 44:31.082
Yeah, realm buddies.

44:31.116 --> 44:32.877
Would you guys every have
a falling out?

44:32.911 --> 44:34.637
You know, like, uh,

44:34.672 --> 44:37.882
the guy who's
your best buddy
on the realm,

44:37.916 --> 44:39.918
but then, you just...

44:39.953 --> 44:41.748
Oh, just what?

44:43.542 --> 44:45.544
[SHARPLY]
You don't connect anymore.

44:48.996 --> 44:50.998
Not like you used to.

44:51.033 --> 44:53.518
Look, what your father
is trying to say

44:53.552 --> 44:56.383
is that he would be happier
living alone

44:56.417 --> 44:59.041
with a rubber doll than having
