with you?

45:00.490 --> 45:01.975
Look at your kids, Adam.

45:02.009 --> 45:04.460
You're about to lose
your kids.

45:04.494 --> 45:07.705
Are they not
more important to you
than some stupid avatar?

45:07.739 --> 45:09.568
Do you want me to stay?

45:09.603 --> 45:11.536
