45:56.650 --> 46:00.102
So now, you're diagnosed
with this heart condition,

46:00.136 --> 46:02.656
and you feel
like the only way
you can die in peace

46:02.690 --> 46:06.453
is to get your company ahead
with some CHIP technology

46:06.487 --> 46:09.767
