we're all connected.

46:24.471 --> 46:26.714
Not necessarily
in a religious sense.

46:27.854 --> 46:31.512
But more in terms
of some...

46:31.547 --> 46:32.928
collective fate.

46:32.962 --> 46:35.516
Please consider
the random nature

46:35.551 --> 46:36.863
of our creation.

46:36.897 --> 46:39.624
What if my mom
had missed her train

46:39.658 --> 46:42.040
the day she met
my father?

46:42.075 --> 46:45.216
Would somebody else be born
to create Premium 3,

46:45.250 --> 46:47.735
and affect
the order of your life

46:47.770 --> 46:50.842
in the same way
that you, say, I have?

46:50.877 --> 46:53.224
[SIGHS]
