1:38:21.861 --> 1:38:24.277
Oh, my God.

1:38:24.312 --> 1:38:25.278
I missed you.

1:38:25.313 --> 1:38:26.901
I missed you too, baby.

1:38:26.935 --> 1:38:28.281
Did you?

1:38:32.078 --> 1:38:34.184
-What?
-Nothing.

1:38:34.218 --> 1:38:36.255
I-I just
remember those differently.

1:38:36.289 --> 1:38:38.671
-[LAUGHS]
-Are you disappointed?

1:38:38.705 --> 1:38:40.052
Just surprised.

1:38:40.086 --> 1:38:41.260
In a good way.

1:38:41.294 --> 1:38:43.158
Well, good. Heh.

1:38:47.887 --> 1:38:49.544
