1:38:56.620 --> 1:38:58.725
We should get back
to the house.

1:38:58.760 --> 1:39:01.314
The kids are there.
I miss them.

1:39:01.349 --> 1:39:02.971
Really?

1:39:03.006 --> 1:39:06.285
I don't remember you
being the homely type.

1:39:06.319 --> 1:39:08.218
I've changed.

1:39:08.252 --> 1:39:09.736
I'm a better man now.

1:39:11.117 --> 1:39:14.293
Oh, boy,
you sure are...

1:39:14.327 --> 1:39:16.674
I guess we're
both better now.

1:39:16.709 --> 1:39:20.955
Oh, my God, I don't think
I've ever felt this good.

1:39:20.989 --> 1:39:23.233
And-and I don't think
that I have ever

1:39:23.267 --> 1:39:25.166
loved you more than I do
right now.

1:39:25.200 --> 1:39:26.650
Me too.

1:39:31.206 --> 1:39:33.346
[GASPS]
Oh, my God.

1:39:33.381 --> 1:39:36.004
Premium 3 is gonna
save the world.

1:39:36.039 --> 1:39:38.627
Yeah. If only we can
just replace everyone.

1:39:41.423 --> 1:39:44.012
Well, it's not
such a bad idea.

1:39:44.047 --> 1:39:45.945
-We could start with the kids.
-Yeah, right?

1:39:45.980 --> 1:39:47.222
Feed 'em an overdose
of Lithium X,

1:39:47.257 --> 1:39:48.775
