a bit more compassion.

1:39:55.368 --> 1:40:00.097
And Joshua is
a touch too sensitive.

1:40:01.064 --> 1:40:02.065
What about Nate?

1:40:02.099 --> 1:40:03.687
If we think hard enough,

1:40:03.721 --> 1:40:05.240
I'm sure
we can find something

1:40:05.275 --> 1:40:06.793
to improve in him too.

1:40:06.828 --> 1:40:09.072
We can be the first family
of clones.

1:40:09.106 --> 1:40:10.073
Yes.

1:40:11.384 --> 1:40:13.731
We will win.

1:40:13.766 --> 1:40:16.769
Well, until something else
comes along.

